; task 72, sign-off find: a SOFT likelihood (observe mass strictly between 0
; and 1) makes the posterior's float sums order-sensitive — the interpreter
; folds its cons-prepended run list, so the additions run in reverse
; chronological order, and the native driver must sum the same way or the
; full-precision rendering drifts by one ULP.
(app (var dist.sample-lw)
  (lam ()
    (let nonrec (pvar c) (app (var sample) (app (var bernoulli) (lit 0.5)))
      (let nonrec (pwild)
        (app (var observe) (app (var bernoulli) (lit 0.7)) (var c))
        (var c))))
  (lit 500) (lit 42))
